title: Arnette Eyewear's Multiple Personality Disorder -- Skate -- New York City
description:
In the second episode of Arnette's Multiple Personality Disorder - Skate Series, the team hopped into a fifteen passenger van and drove their way from North Carolina up to New York City for some good old fashioned city street skating. Typical mayhem ensued, with the crew destroying spots and and even busting out some old school tricks. Pretty standard when you have such a mix of guys on one team.

Sit back, relax, and enjoy the latest episode of Arnette's Multiple Personality Disorder series.

#LIVEARNETTE
